{% extends "design-system.njk" %}
{% set title = 'Colors' %}
{% set summary %}
Colors are set with design tokens, which are located here: `src/site/_data/design/tokens.json`. 
There is also a contextual relationship between colors and how they are applied with themes: `src/site/_data/design/themes.js`

